683
00:48:05,905 --> 00:48:07,740
She left.

684
00:48:14,288 --> 00:48:15,665
Okay.

685
00:48:24,006 --> 00:48:25,675
Okay.

686
00:48:27,009 --> 00:48:29,345
This sound woke me up.

687
00:48:31,472 --> 00:48:33,933
At first I didn't know what it was.

688
00:48:35,059 --> 00:48:38,104
Sounded like an animal
that got trapped.

689
00:48:40,523 --> 00:48:43,359
I never heard a man cry before.

690
00:48:45,319 --> 00:48:48,114
I came downstairs in my underwear.

691
00:48:49,282 --> 00:48:51,868
I see my father in the kitchen.

692
00:48:52,368 --> 00:48:54,620
