if they'd seen my mother.

711
00:50:11,822 --> 00:50:13,616
Her name was Doris.

712
00:50:13,783 --> 00:50:18,955
My grandmother had a place
that's a restaurant in Tangerine, Florida.

713
00:50:19,121 --> 00:50:21,999
So I used to imagine
maybe that's where she went.

714
00:50:23,209 --> 00:50:28,965
Then I came to terms with the fact
that doesn't really matter, you know?

715
00:50:29,215 --> 00:50:33,719
Wherever she went,
she had a good reason to leave here.

716
00:50:34,845 --> 00:50:37,682
She didn't wanna be
my mother anymore...

717
00:50:38,182 --> 00:50:42,353
...and she wasn't coming back.

718
00:50:44,939 --> 00:50:48,317
