720
00:50:52,822 --> 00:50:55,157
How bad can it be?

721
00:51:05,501 --> 00:51:07,920
Oh, yeah.

722
00:51:23,185 --> 00:51:24,395
<i>Desmond Elden.</i>

723
00:51:24,562 --> 00:51:28,274
<i>Systems tech at Vericom,
22 years old.</i>

724
00:51:28,899 --> 00:51:32,194
